{% set pageTitle = "" %}
{% set pageDescription = "" %}
{% set landingPage = true %}
{% set theme = "Principles" %}
{% set hideBreadcrumb = true %}
{% set hideSideNav = true %}

{% extends "app-layout-two-thirds.njk" %}

{% block breadcrumb %}{% endblock %}

{% block outerBody %}
<section class="ofh-hero-ds ofh-hero-ds--image ofh-hero-ds--image-description" style="background-image: url('/assets/ds-hero-dots-green.svg');" aria-label="Hero section">
    <div class="ofh-width-container app-width-container">
      <div class="ofh-grid-row">
        <div class="ofh-grid-column-two-thirds">
          <div class="ofh-hero-ds__wrapper app-hero__wrapper">
            <h1 class="ofh-u-margin-bottom-4">Design principles</h1>
            <p class="ofh-body-l ofh-u-margin-bottom-1">These principles guide all of our design. Use them to get started on a project and to help with making decisions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
  
 {% block bodyContent %}
  <ol class="featured-list">
    <li class="featured-list--item">
      <div class="featured-list--item__content">
        <span class="featured-list--item__number featured-list--item__number--mobile ofh-heading-l">1</span>
        <h2 class="featured-list--item__heading "><span class="featured-list--item__number ofh-heading-l ofh-u-margin-bottom-1">1</span>We design to innovate</h2>
        <h3>What:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">We learn from evidence and the expertise all around us.</p>
        <p>This helps us take bold, innovative approaches that make a measurable impact. We are not afraid of a challenge.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>How:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Experiment and learn all the time.</p>
        <p>Look inside and outside Our Future Health for inspiration. Work within ethical and legal frameworks. And do not be afraid to fail. Every time we fail, we learn.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>Why:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">No one has done what we're doing now.</p>
        <p>Our innovation inspires the whole organisation. And paves the way for success.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="featured-list--item">
      <div class="featured-list--item__content">
        <span class="featured-list--item__number featured-list--item__number--mobile ofh-heading-l">2</span>
        <h2 class="featured-list--item__heading "><span class="featured-list--item__number ofh-heading-l ofh-u-margin-bottom-1">2</span>We design for everyone</h2>
        <h3>What:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Everyone has something unique to contribute.</p>
        <p>And we respect every single one of them. From researchers to participants, all of our users play a pivotal role in our success.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>How:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Take the time to understand what motivates and inspires your users.</p>
        <p>And what their challenges are. Listen to them. Learn from them. Design with them. Prioritise diversity and inclusion at every step. Do not make assumptions about what you think is 'right' for them.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>Why:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Real people use our products.</p>
        <p>Prioritise and respect them. And we can make products that that are valuable for everyone.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="featured-list--item">
      <div class="featured-list--item__content">
        <span class="featured-list--item__number featured-list--item__number--mobile ofh-heading-l">3</span>
        <h2 class="featured-list--item__heading "><span class="featured-list--item__number ofh-heading-l ofh-u-margin-bottom-1">3</span>We design for inclusivity</h2>
        <h3>What:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">We acknowledge that design has the potential to create barriers.</p>
        <p>We break them down. And reduce friction so everyone can play their part in groundbreaking research and enhance the robustness of our research.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>How:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Consult best practice and guidelines.</p>
        <p>Critique designs from every possible perspective. Work with users to test products. Do not make assumptions about our user's abilities or limitations. But work with users to remove barriers.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>Why:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Everybody should have the opportunity to be a part of Our Future Health.</p>
        <p>To be a part of something bigger than themselves and to have impact for generations to come.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="featured-list--item">
      <div class="featured-list--item__content">
        <span class="featured-list--item__number featured-list--item__number--mobile ofh-heading-l">4</span>
        <h2 class="featured-list--item__heading "><span class="featured-list--item__number ofh-heading-l ofh-u-margin-bottom-1">4</span>We design for clarity</h2>
        <h3>What:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">We make things understandable for our users.</p>
        <p>We break down complex tasks to create frictionless user journeys.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>How:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Be consistent.</p>
        <p>Address user expectations through the interface and content. And balance functionality with on-brand and well-crafted designs. Be mindful of the product you're working on and the needs of it's users.</p>
        <hr class="ofh-u-margin-top-2 ofh-u-margin-bottom-6">
        <h3>Why:</h3>
        <p class="ofh-u-font-weight-bold">Our products must help and motivate our users to complete their task.</p>
        <p>If we reduce cognitive load, we will create more engaging, valuable and successful interactions with our users.</p>
      </div>
    </li> 
    </ol>
   

{% endblock %}